{"tid":470853,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果對數字敏感？真心求教","createTime":"2017-11-16T16:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T05:15:42.000Z","uid":64797,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff9fae848c61d9d53be7378749365a78a643c9b","tid":470853,"uid":64797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"姨甥女而家二年班，數學科麻麻，對數字不太敏感<br />\n有咩遊戲/工具可以令佢對數字有多啲興趣？<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e953beeeed12a66a404eed39a2d2210e271bde","tid":470853,"uid":107157,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T22:58:21.000Z","msg":"要搵到佢既g點，再加以調教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec9bc501fc3566193c0d69cd7597ca96ecfcfb9","tid":470853,"uid":64797,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要搵到佢既g點，再加以調教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係咪要話好撚好笑？"},{"pid":"9c5a1a8b7928c914e78244b76b4e8a4f2471b7d0","tid":470853,"uid":50428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"玩下24個D  姐係 4張POKER +-X*到24, 當然仲可以加多D符號, 上網應該大把<br />\n<br />\n小校園個D小遊戲<br />\n<br />\n當年都係玩呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e302a1ca70e81eeac7f916c19a57fa889496dad6","tid":470853,"uid":50428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:37:27.000Z","msg":"大個D可以玩D Logic game, 過河,橋游戲。<br />\n<br />\nBoardgame既話 rummikub ? 魔力橋姐係,  幾個人陪佢玩都正"},{"pid":"0ea8a27347dd0afab61d6ead0568780e4176e744","tid":470853,"uid":64797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大個D可以玩D Logic game, 過河,橋游戲。<br />\n<br />\nBoardgame既話 rummikub ? 魔力橋姐係,  幾個人陪佢玩都正</blockquote><br />\n我個姨甥女二年班咋，我都係一個星期見佢一次<br />\n又唔想就咁買本補充俾佢做<br />\n等我都睇下除左24之外仲有冇啲咩game可以同佢玩下<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df50fdd7922d753897f510de9a7cfdb38d8bbaf1","tid":470853,"uid":79686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"教佢programming<br />\n<br />\n要學好數先要學logic<br />\n<br />\n學好個logic 數啲野 一點就明"},{"pid":"806fd875869b1a4ba39fa66caeffe002748d2488","tid":470853,"uid":66391,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"如果對數字敏感～就唔好掂d數字囉～"},{"pid":"5ddd652b0869b8301f8ef26033669d3776fca838","tid":470853,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要搵到佢既g點，再加以調教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係咪要話好撚好笑？</blockquote><br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得你教極人都唔識<br />\n人類學習最大原動力就係靠腦高潮，而求知方面最大既高潮就係對未知既求知慾。而係香港社會，因為好多負面既因素連帶住學習，e.g.挫敗感，強逼性學習，都令唔少人見到學習就產生負面情緒，以致大腦啟動左防護機制令到條友學極都學唔識野。<br />\n所以，要搵到學生係學習上邊一方面會得到高潮感，就可以令佢自己更容易學習。<br />\n學術台之前有個post講潛意識學習，有埋文獻。<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，比埋啲咩合24人玩，人地明明無興趣玩，又點會吸收到知識，所以教人最緊要搵到佢既g點。<br />\n<br />\n所以，樓主你黎搞笑? 我句野邊一忽有笑點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25457699e30aefc41fe0c51f9a1bece5b4ac49b6","tid":470853,"uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T20:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要搵到佢既g點，再加以調教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係咪要話好撚好笑？</blockquote><br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得你教極人都唔識<br />\n人類學習最大原動力就係靠腦高潮，而求知方面最大既高潮就係對未知既求知慾。而係香港社會，因為好多負面既因素連帶住學習，e.g.挫敗感，強逼性學習，都令唔少人見到學習就產生負面情緒，以致大腦啟動左防護機制令到條友學極都學唔識野。<br />\n所以，要搵到學生係學習上邊一方面會得到高潮感，就可以令佢自己更容易學習。<br />\n學術台之前有個post講潛意識學習，有埋文獻。<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，比埋啲咩合24人玩，人地明明無興趣玩，又點會吸收到知識，所以教人最緊要搵到佢既g點。<br />\n<br />\n所以，樓主你黎搞笑? 我句野邊一忽有笑點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n妄想係網上討論區點化香港人已經係最大笑點 ching由佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308f2ce2622996b75cf870698e9c6e1955fe9389","tid":470853,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T21:19:35.000Z","msg":"對數字敏感即係點？見到數字會出紅疹？會呼吸困難？會流鼻水同眼類？"},{"pid":"fd63a91ab659d2d40a5a7bb058eb10fcd1a4208c","tid":470853,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T21:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對數字敏感即係點？見到數字會出紅疹？會呼吸困難？會流鼻水同眼類？</blockquote><br />\n認真mode：要小朋友對數學有興趣可以搵同數學有關，小朋友又鐘意嘅野入手，例如故事，卡通，遊戲，唔好淨係focus響功課方面：<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/bookseries/B00YSJXE7A/ref=dp_st_1570911525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fbookseries%2FB00YSJXE7A%2Fref%3Ddp_st_1570911525&d=q81vSNv%2F1E6q%2FqP0JqdngiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=12d97b83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/bookseries/B00YSJXE7A/ref=dp_st_1570911525</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pbskids.org/cyberchase/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpbskids.org%2Fcyberchase%2F&d=q81vSNv%2F1E6q%2FqP0JqdngiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b80515f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://pbskids.org/cyberchase/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外平時日常生活上可以同小朋友示範數學應用，例如買野計價錢。"},{"pid":"501fd458fc661bf4761f1355489a019f00406e43","tid":470853,"uid":75457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T21:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jc1fugrn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjc1fugrn&h=a0c9fd65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b30820a47751f196f572f68ad3442deb92a4977","tid":470853,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T21:47:56.000Z","msg":"好似話學樂器同麻雀都有幫助<br />\n用啲小遊戲令佢提起學習興趣？<br />\n<br />\nPS. 有研究話好多女仔由細到大被灌輸佢哋數理唔夠男仔好呢個歪念<br />\n所以對stem 興趣唔大<br />\n呢種性別定形同歧視由小學已經開始<br />\n希望你姨甥女唔係其中一個受害者<br />\n<br />\n出到嚟做嘢佢哋見你係女都會低估你數字邏輯之類能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8547ddf76e5961f65496dfb9de6eacb320b7cac","tid":470853,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"試下玩數獨"}]}